## 최적화 방안

### [최적화 1] Fetch Join으로 N+1 제거

**After - JPQL Fetch Join + DTO Projection**

```kotlin
// CallQueueRepository.kt
interface CallQueueRepository : JpaRepository<CallQueueEntity, String> {

    // Before: N+1 발생
    fun findByStatus(status: CallQueueStatus): List<CallQueueEntity>

    // After: Fetch Join으로 단일 쿼리
    @Query("""
        SELECT q FROM CallQueueEntity q
        JOIN FETCH q.userProfile p
        JOIN FETCH p.preference pref
        WHERE q.status = :status
          AND q.expiredAt > :now
        ORDER BY q.createdAt ASC
    """)
    fun findWaitingWithProfiles(
        status: CallQueueStatus,
        now: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now()
    ): List<CallQueueEntity>
}
```

```kotlin
// QueryDSL Projection 활용 (복잡한 필터링 조건)
@Repository
class CallMatchingQueryRepository(private val queryFactory: JPAQueryFactory) {

    fun findMatchCandidates(
        userId: String,
        filter: MatchingFilter
    ): List<MatchCandidateDto> {
        val queue = QCallQueueEntity.callQueueEntity
        val profile = QUserProfileEntity.userProfileEntity
        val pref = QUserPreferenceEntity.userPreferenceEntity

        return queryFactory
            .select(
                Projections.constructor(
                    MatchCandidateDto::class.java,
                    queue.userId,
                    profile.nickname,
                    profile.age,
                    profile.region,
                    pref.interests
                )
            )
            .from(queue)
            .innerJoin(profile).on(queue.userId.eq(profile.userId))
            .innerJoin(pref).on(profile.userId.eq(pref.userId))
            .where(
                queue.status.eq(CallQueueStatus.WAITING),
                queue.userId.ne(userId),
                queue.expiredAt.gt(LocalDateTime.now()),
                ageRangeFilter(filter.ageMin, filter.ageMax, profile),
                regionFilter(filter.region, profile),
                notBlocked(userId, queue.userId)
            )
            .limit(50) // 후보군 상한 설정
            .fetch()
    }
}
```

예상 개선: 쿼리 수 101회 -> 1회, 응답 시간 ~2,000ms -> ~80ms (95% 감소).

